ActCanada Business Corporations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canada Business Corporations Regulations, 2001
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA BUSINESS CORPORATIONS REGULATIONS, 2001 in order to (1) better align service fees under the Canada Business Corporation Act with the cost of delivering the services; (2) encourage the use of low-cost services delivery methods; (3) promote compliance with the Canada Business Corporation Act; and (4) support greater corporate transparency.
